lockquote>我上年in 我地個班有人考試入去 有人in入去 如果要考試內容大約係英文 數學同相關學科題目 全英 努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有筆試？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁大獲，男朋友英文好唔掂...英數係dse lv？<br />\n<br />\nBf 係先幾年fd畢業，呢兩年做緊相關嘅嘢，所以諗住繼續進修入返u(我讀緊u)，但佢英文真係好差....係咪機會好微</blockquote><br />\n學歷吾夠就有考試 大約英文就中三程度 數就大約中五不過選擇題 全英卷 要睇得明題目對英文差係有難度 吾知你報邊間 不過記住一次吾得都好 再叫你去補考一定要去 好多時收吾夠人都係最尾個次鬆手啲 我自己都英文白痴 會考都冇考過 做幾年野入反去讀hd 英文拎d都生存到 所以其實你bf肯讀就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c1eef03c836dacf4dbdbd78dbc2b316d446428","tid":307124,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"Civil hd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bde1e74bcb9f65fd21ea7ebbfd710caac4afa71","tid":307124,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Civil hd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAll in computer engineering la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbb63acece2c9d1e0adf4f53ce75c45b7c0c46c","tid":307124,"uid":122446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"報bse hd收到信去interview"},{"pid":"26a6f7e9cb45617988bb93a18afc8809edcec10c","tid":307124,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報bse hd收到信去interview</blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我志在參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係讀工程既料"},{"pid":"e75222e7157fa30aa8c871c057dc5d5915bfa403","tid":307124,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:55:18.000Z",